    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small lightweight motorcycles that are very similar to a bicycle, but propelled by an attached motor. The specific features and capacity may be defined differently in various legislative districts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
